<item>
            <title>[SENTRY-408] The URI permission should support more filesystem prefixes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SENTRY-408</link>
                <project id="12314720" key="SENTRY">Sentry (Retired)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the URI privilege validation assumes that the filesystem prefixes can be &apos;file:&apos; or &apos;hdfs:&apos;. We should make this more generic to support other prefixes available in the underlying filesystem.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
